                    "line_text": "Toute la nuit, grâce à la lune",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "« Clartive » alors, et dont le front",
