                    "line_text": "Proclament jusques à l’excès",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Le soleil… qui plus tard se lève,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jusqu’à l’aube en peu d’ombre, et ces\nChante-clair, clair comme un beau rêve,\nProclament jusques à l’excès\nLe soleil… qui plus tard se lève,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Trop tard pour ceux qui sont reclus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Au poulailler, – tout comme une âme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ne tendant que vers les élus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Dans le péché, prison infâme, –",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Trop tard pour ceux qui sont reclus\nAu poulailler, – tout comme une âme\nNe tendant que vers les élus,\nDans le péché, prison infâme, –"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et comme une âme les bons coqs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Vigilants, tels au temps de Pierre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Souffrent, mais, en dépit des chocs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "D’ombre, chantent, et l’âme espère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
